item.title: Dave Ramsey: 6 Biggest Retirement Myths You Shouldn’t Believe
Michelle Obama responds to Trump "Black jobs" comments at DNC
item.description: Former first lady Michelle Obama joined former President Barack Obama at the Democratic National Convention in Chicago Tuesday. During her speech, Michelle Obama responded to former President Donald Trump's comments about race at the National Association of Black Journalists conference. CBS News campaign reporter Shawna Mizelle reports.
